OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police is still
OL,8,Fmissing nearly half of its officers'
OL,9,FDNA from its database, and more than a
OL,10,Ffifth of their fingerprints.
OL,12,FElimination databases are used to
OL,13,Fexclude police officers' DNA or
OL,14,Ffingerprints from crime scene samples,
OL,15,Fhelping to prevent contamination from
OL,16,Fbeing mistaken for a suspect's profile.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
