OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FHowever, the missing data could also
OL,8,Fhamper the force's ability to catch
OL,9,Fcriminals in their own ranks, like
OL,10,FWayne Couzens, a police officer who
OL,11,Fraped and murdered Sarah Everard in
OL,12,F2021.
OL,14,FOf the 32,431 Met Police officers,
OL,15,F17,458 have their DNA on the force's
OL,16,Felimination database, which is just
OL,17,F53.8%.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, 25,802 officers have their
OL,20,Ffingerprints on the elimination
OL,21,Fdatabase, which is 79.6%.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
