CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FIn November 2024, the London Standard
OL,8,Freported that around half of the Met's
OL,9,Fofficers could be missing from its own
OL,10,FDNA and fingerprint databases.
OL,12,FA Met Police spokesperson said at the
OL,13,Ftime: "We're in the process of
OL,14,Fassessing those samples we don't
OL,15,Fcurrently hold and ensuring our
OL,16,Fprocesses to collect them are robust
OL,17,Fand effective.
OL,19,F"We expect this work to conclude in
OL,20,Fthe next 12 months."
OL,26,@uD@GOU{D@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FIt is understood a new database has
OL,8,Fbeen established to track the career
OL,9,Flifecycle of biometric data samples
OL,10,Fassociated with serving officers to
OL,11,Fensure continuity and the Met is
OL,12,F"confident" its processes have been
OL,13,Fassured.
OL,15,FThe Met also says it has developed a
OL,16,Fmore reliable data process to identify
OL,17,Findividuals whose data is missing,
OL,18,Faddressing legacy records and data
OL,19,Fquality issues, including identifying
OL,20,Fduplicate records for the same person.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FThat said, the percentage of officers
OL,8,Fwith their DNA on file has risen very
OL,9,Flittle in the 15 months since November
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FScotland Yard says it aims to ensure
OL,13,Fthat the DNA and fingerprints for
OL,14,Fevery serving police officer in the
OL,15,FMetropolitan Police and Met Special
OL,16,FConstabulary are collected, recorded
OL,17,Fand uploaded to the elimination
OL,18,Fdatabase by March 31, 2028.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
