CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FLabour former minister Dawn Butler
OL,8,Ftold the Press Association it is
OL,9,F"deeply disappointing" that progress
OL,10,Fhas been slow on ensuring that
OL,11,Fbiometric data of all officers are
OL,12,Frecorded, which she said is an
OL,13,F"essential safeguard to help restore
OL,14,Fconfidence in our police service".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]uD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
