OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,FThe Brent MP said: "I have long pushed
OL,8,Ffor the Met Police to ensure that the
OL,9,FDNA and fingerprints of every single
OL,10,Fserving officer are properly recorded
OL,11,Fon the database, so it is deeply
OL,12,Fdisappointing to learn that progress
OL,13,Fhas been slow.
OL,15,F"There can be no more delay ` the Met
OL,16,Fmust now act with urgency to ensure
OL,17,Fevery officer is included.
OL,26,@oD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
