FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772565069
OL,3,CMetropolitan Police still missing
OL,4,Cnearly half of its officers' DNA from
OL,5,Cdatabase
OL,7,F"This is essential for crime
OL,8,Felimination when DNA is inadvertently
OL,9,Fleft at a scene, but it's also about
OL,10,Faccountability, transparency and
OL,11,Frebuilding public trust after the
OL,12,Fserious cases of police misconduct in
OL,13,Frecent years."
OL,15,FHolding this information is an
OL,16,Fessential safeguard to help restore
OL,17,Fconfidence in our police service,
OL,18,Fwhich will benefit the many amazing
OL,19,Fofficers too."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@NOU{D@NO]
